    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>HAPPY BEGINNING</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <byline class="print_byline">By PATRICK McGEEHAN</byline>
      <byline class="normalized_byline">Mcgeehan, Patrick</byline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Qualcomm director Sherry Lansing was hired shortly before company ended practice of giving each new director 40,000 stock options; also benefited from policy of doubling annual fee from $100,000 to $50,000 (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>It's a coincidence that only a Hollywood screenwriter could dream up.</p>
        <p>Sherry Lansing, the first woman to run a major Hollywood studio, became a director of Qualcomm, the wireless technology company, in September, just before it decided to stop giving each new director 40,000 stock options.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>It's a coincidence that only a Hollywood screenwriter could dream up.</p>
        <p>Sherry Lansing, the first woman to run a major Hollywood studio, became a director of Qualcomm, the wireless technology company, in September, just before it decided to stop giving each new director 40,000 stock options.</p>
        <p>At the same time, Qualcomm doubled each director's annual fee to $100,000 from $50,000. She was just in time to benefit from both.</p>
        <p>PATRICK McGEEHAN</p>
        <p>OPENERS: SUITS</p>
      </block>
